high_descs: Turn right to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and take a knife from it and close the door
Turn back and walk towards the table
Cut an apple into pieces
Hold the knife in the hand
Place the knife at the bottom side of the table
Look at the cut apple now
Take a piece of apple from the cut apple
Turn back and walk straight and again take a right turn and reach the microwave oven by turning right side
Open the oven and put the apple piece inside it and close it and after few seconds of processing, open the oven and take the piece out and close the oven
Turn right and walk straight and again take a right turn to reach the fridge
Put the apple piece inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the apple piece inside the fridge

high_descs: Turn right to the fridge immediately ahead of you.
Remove the knife from the fridge.
Turn around from the fridge and approach the white dining table just ahead.
Slice the potato that's in the middle of the table.
Look down towards the edge of the table near you.
Place the knife down on the table.
Look back towards the potato you just sliced.
Pick up one slice of the potato.
Turn around and go back to the fridge, then take a right and stop at the microwave on the right.
Use the microwave on the potato slice and pick it back up.
Go back to the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato slice in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the fridge.
Pick up the knife from the fridge.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Cut the potato with the knife.
Look down to face the dining table.
Put the knife on the dining table.
Look up to reach the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from the dining table.
Turn around and head to the microwave on the right.
Heat the slice of potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Put the slice of potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of potato in the fridge.
